ghost-role-information-drone-name = Maintenance Drone
# Goobstation
ghost-role-information-drone-description = Maintain the station. You may interact with others if you do not disrupt them or create problems. You may ask for help and follow reasonable orders. Use +/+d to talk in the Dronemind.
ghost-role-information-drone-rules = You are bound by these laws both in-game and out-of-character:

     1. You may interact with other beings, ask for help, and follow orders, provided this does not disrupt them, create problems, or conflict with your other laws.
     2. Your goal is to maintain or improve the station to the best of your ability.
     3. You may not take any action which causes damage or harm to the station or its inhabitants.
